title: Amigo The Devil Hates Vodka, Loves Good Bourbon And Talks About His Time on Tinder
itunes:title: Amigo The Devil Hates Vodka, Loves Good Bourbon And Talks About His Time on Tinder
description:
Is he country? Death metal? Or acoustic genius? Amigo The Devil is a brilliant musician who doesn't exactly fit in a genre with his guitar and hard lyrics. He's also one helluva conversationalist. And like Fred, he hates vodka. Good man! As they sip Old Fitzgerald Birthday Bourbon and Belle Meade Bourbon, they talk about why vodka sucks, food favorites (including nuts) and why Amigo will never drink a martini.
